# See https://help.github.com/articles/ignoring-files/ for more about ignoring files.

# Test output — generated at runtime, never commit
test-results/playwright-report/
test-results/playwright-output/
test-results/*.json
test-results/*.mp4
test-results/screenshots/
test-results/videos/
# Keep the directory itself and static reports
!test-results/.gitkeep
!test-results/dev-test-report.md
!test-results/security-findings.md
!test-results/performance-summary.md

# Playwright
playwright-report/
playwright/.cache/

